title: Day One Highlights - Volcom Pipe Pro 2012
description:
After an action packed morning that saw a huge, shifting, NW swell at Pipe, the event was deemed incontestable at 10:30 am and has been cancelled for the day.. Here are some of the highlights from before the contest was called off.

- Music - 
Song: "Old Ghost"
Artist: The Lovely Bad Things
Release: New Ghost / Old Waves
